    "sketchCode": "// Example: IR Receiver\n// Decode infrared remote signals on pin 11.\n\n#include <IRremote.h>\n\nint recvPin = 11;\nIRrecv irrecv(recvPin);\n\nvoid setup() {\n  Serial.begin(9600);\n  irrecv.enableIRIn();\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  if (irrecv.decode()) {\n    Serial.print(\"IR Code: 0x\");\n    Serial.println(irrecv.decodedIRData.decodedRawData, HEX);\n    irrecv.resume();\n  }\n  delay(100);\n}\n",
